name: Premium Burp Cloths - 2 Piece Set, Bloom/Mint Dots
description:
Each burp cloth consists of a 6-ply Premium cloth diaper, accented with the patterned fabric. 

Size: approximately 13"x19", perfect size to throw in your diaper bag as a changing pad too!

100% Cotton

Machine Wash Gentle, Tumble Dry Low.
Do not use chlorine bleach.

Quality materials, delicious prints.

Great Baby Shower or New Baby Gift.
